HEADWORD: Intentional
<hw>In*ten"tion*al</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>intentionnel</ets>.]</ety> <def>Done by intention or design;
intended; designed; <as>as, the act was <ex>intentional</ex>, not
accidental</as>. Opposite of <ant>unintentional</ant> or
<ant>unintended</ant>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Intentionality</ent>⟦br⟧
